description:
I WILL WIN! Our 28th Ultimate 30-Minute Motivational Speech Compilation is here! These are some of the BEST Motivational Speeches you'll ever hear, featuring powerful speeches from Marcus Elevation Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Dr. Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity), Freddy Fri (https://bit.ly/FreddyFriMotiversity) and many more!


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/), Paul Elhart (http://bit.ly/2SiEaIN), Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine), and Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
